ter of the Dean of Christ Church, Oxford."],"variants":[{"name":"Alys","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Alice ."]},{"name":"Alis","meanings":["equivalent of <b>Alice</b> ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Alice Knoell was born in 1470, in Somerset, England, United Kingdom, her father, William Knoell, was 15 and her mother, Joan Champney, was 15. She had at least 1 son with John Portman. She died in 1559, in Somerset, Bristol, Massachusetts, United States, at the age of 89."},"et":{"1470–1559":"1470–1559","1475–Male":"1475–Surnud","1445–1521":"1445–1521","1496–1557":"1496–1557","1455–Male":"1455–Surnud","1455–1540":"1455–1540","1557":"1557","1445":"1445","1455":"1455","1521":"1521","1475":"1475","1496":"1496","1540":"1540","Bef. 1540":"enne 1540","1470":"1470","5 jun 1521":"5. juuni 1521","5 February 1557":"5. veebruar 1557","1559":"1559","Samford Orcas, Somerset, England":"Somerset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","London, London, England":"London, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"England","Bristol, Somerset, England":"Somerset, Bristol, Massachusetts, Ameerika Ühendriigid","Frome, Somerset, England":"Frome, Somerset, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1470–1559":"1470–1559","1475–Male":"1475–Kuollut","1445–1521":"1445–1521","1496–1557":"1496–1557","1455–Male":"1455–Kuollut","1455–1540":"1455–1540","1557":"1557","1445":"1445","1455":"1455","1521":"1521","1475":"1475","1496":"1496","1540":"1540","Bef. 1540":"ennen vuotta 1540","1470":"1470","5 jun 1521":"5. kesäkuuta 1521","5 February 1557":"5. helmikuuta 1557","1559":"1559","Samford Orcas, Somerset, England":"Somerset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","London, London, England":"London, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"England","Bristol, Somerset, England":"Somerset, Bristol, Massachusetts, Yhdysvallat","Frome, Somerset, England":"Frome, Somerset, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1470–1559":"1470–1559","1475–Male":"1475–Décédé","1445–1521":"1445–1521","1496–1557":"1496–1557","1455–Male":"1455–D